<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"></head>
<body style="font-family:sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px">
<p>Hello <strong>{{.UserName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  The <strong>{{.DeadlineKind}}</strong> deadline for
  <strong>{{.ConferenceName}} ({{.ConferenceAcronym}})</strong>
  is in <strong>{{.LeadTimeDays}} day(s)</strong>,
  on <strong>{{formatDate .DeadlineDate}}</strong>.
</p>
<p>Log in to Confero to review your starred conferences.</p>
<p style="color:#666;font-size:0.85em">- Confero</p>
</body>
</html>
